---
const beforeImage = '/images/male-transformation-before.jpg';
const afterImage = '/images/male-transformation-after.jpg';
---

<section class="relative bg-gray-900 py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Before/After Images -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-xl">
            <div class="aspect-w-3 aspect-h-4">
              <img 
                src={beforeImage}
                alt="Before transformation" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                width="400"
                height="600"
                loading="eager"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="absolute top-4 left-4">
              <span class="text-white text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shadow">Before</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-xl">
            <div class="aspect-w-3 aspect-h-4">
              <img 
                src={afterImage}
                alt="After transformation" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                width="400"
                height="600"
                loading="eager"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="absolute top-4 left-4">
              <span class="text-white text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1 bg-green-600 rounded-full shadow">After</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl mb-8">
          Transform Your Life After 40
        </h1>
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert">
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            This site is a comprehensive resource for all men over 40 years old who are looking to transform their physique, energy levels, and libido and become the timeless masculine machine they always intended to be.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            As we age, numerous external and internal factors combine to affect us and lead to fatigue, listlessness, weakness, depression, and a feeling of malaise. The formula to reverse this is not complex, it just requires honest and accurate assessment and resolution.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The most critical factor is replacement of youthful testosterone levels. Beyond Testosterone Replacement, supervised by a licensed provider, strength training and diet optimization are important as well, and several other factors contribute such as quality of sleep, stress management, and others.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Utilize the below tools and calculators to begin your journey to transform into the ultimate male you, join our community of like minded guys to discuss and collaborate, and schedule a booking call to discuss our 12 month guaranteed transformation program based on 1 on 1 personal coaching and supervision.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4">
            <a href="https://calendly.com/support-34zs/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
              Schedule Consultation
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="#fitness-tools" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors">
              Explore Tools
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 10.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-6-6a1 1 0 111.414-1.414L9 14.586V3a1 1 0 012 0v11.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
